org.nerd4j.csv.registry

Class CSVRegistry

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.nerd4j.csv.registry.CSVRegistry

  • public final class CSVRegistry
extends Object
    Represents a registry containing the provider able to understand the configured values and provide the related objects.

    This object represents a facade to access the following actual registry:

    • CSVFieldValidatorRegistry
    • CSVFieldConverterRegistry
    • CSVToModelBinderFactoryRegistry
    • ModelToCSVBinderFactoryRegistry
